> DECISION:                     ACCEPTED
> Proposal Name:                Odoo ERP Project
> Название предложения проекта: Проект Odoo ERP
> Professor:                    Hadi Saleh

> Proposal Project Type: Final Qualifying Work (ВКР)
> Format:                Project
> Language:              English

> PROPOSED BY:      SEFA ŞENLİK
> Additional Email: senliksefa@gmail.com
> Additional Phone: +90 535 654 8572
> Telegram ID:      sefasenlik_ru

> Detailed Description: 
Odoo is a comprehensive and versatile Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) platform that offers a seamless solution for managing the complex processes of handling student Course Projects (КР) and Graduation Theses (ВКР). With its user-friendly interface and robust functionality, Odoo streamlines the entire academic workflow, from project proposal to evaluation and archiving. This ERP system allows educational institutions to efficiently track and manage student projects, assign supervisors, monitor progress, and store relevant documents, ensuring transparency and accountability throughout the process. Moreover, Odoo's reporting and analytics tools enable administrators to gain valuable insights into student performance and the overall productivity of the academic department, making it an indispensable tool for universities and educational organizations seeking to enhance their management of student КР and ВКРs.
> Expected Results: 
- Functional ERP platform to handle student project
- Documentation of the product
- Detailed course work report

